About this TODO list
--------------------

  This file was created when the project was a personal private project.
  That's why there's an "Old TODO list" section at the end.

  This list should contain the most immediate changes to be done.

  My current Lazarus installation:

  Lazarus Version: 1.8.2+dfsg-3
  FPC Version: 3.0.4
  Linux: x86_64-linux-gtk2
  Windows: Windows 7 64bit
           Windows XP 64bit



Bugs
----

 - Auto indentation doesn't work properly.  Should remove spaces from the
   beggining and the end of the line.  Also it messes up with tabs.
 - Autocompletion should order the suggested words with latest used first.
 - On some desktops (i.e. Linux XFCE) using [Alt]+[Tab] to change window
   doesn't trigger the "lost focus" event.



Feature request
---------------

 - Search and replace.
 - "Save all" to save all modified sources at once.
 - Split editor as Vim.

   This is, allow to have multiple source editors in the same tab so you
   can see different parts of the file at the same time.  Not sure if allow to
   have different files in each one though.



